In this video, we
will answer to the

12
00:00:56,680 --> 00:01:03,220
question why public health engineering matters in
humanitarian crisis. In order to do so,

13
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:05,000
we need to understand the public health

14
00:01:05,090 --> 00:01:09,590
approach that guides humanitarian
assistance of many humanitarian organizations.

15
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:13,680
It will help us to explain
the role of the public health engineering.

16
